NameBaseNotCountry NEnkSuffix AttributiveGenIDef|AttributiveInst # Dir/LR
NameBaseNotCountry NAnkSuffixCaseNc AttributiveGenIDef|AttributiveInst # Dir/LR
NameBaseNotCountry NAnkSuffix AttributiveGenIDef|AttributiveInst # Dir/LR



